<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Let's Go!</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, shrink-to-fit=no" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/index.css" />
</head>

<body>

  <header>
    <h1>Let's Go!</h1>
    <p>Have a trip around the world with us.</p>
  </header>

  <main>

    <div class="topnav">
      <input type="text" style="padding-left: 8px;float: right; width: 25%; height: 46px; background-color: rgb(246, 241, 241)"
        placeholder="Search"/>
      <a href="/" style="float: left">Home</a>
      <a href="/landmarks" style="float: left">Landmarks</a>
      <a href="/countries" style="float: left">Countries</a>
      <a href="/publish" style="float: left">Add a Place</a>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <div class="viewer column" id="viewer">
        <h2 id="placeName">Welcome!</h2>
        <img id="viewImg" src="images/map.svg" class="view-img">
        <p id="placeInfo"></p>
      </div>

      <div class="deck column">
        <div class="card" onmouseover="mouseOver1()" onmouseout="mouseOut()">
          <img id="card1" src="images/1.jpg" alt="Image Not Found!" class="img">
          <h3 id="placeLabel1" class="label">Rizal Park</h3>
          <div class="info">
            <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rizal_Park" style="text-decoration:none;">Read more...</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card" onmouseover="mouseOver2()" onmouseout="mouseOut()">
          <img id="card2" src="images/2.jpg" alt="Image Not Found!" class="img">
          <h3 id="placeLabel2" class="label">Empire State Building</h3>
          <div class="info">
            <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Empire_State_Building" style="text-decoration:none;">Read more...</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card" onmouseover="mouseOver3()" onmouseout="mouseOut()">
          <img id="card3" src="images/3.jpg" alt="Image Not Found!" class="img">
          <h3 id="placeLabel3" class="label">Eiffel Tower</h3>
          <div class="info">
            <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eiffel_Tower" style="text-decoration:none;">Read more...</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card" onmouseover="mouseOver4()" onmouseout="mouseOut()">
          <img id="card4" src="images/4.jpg" alt="Image Not Found!" class="img">
          <h3 id="placeLabel4" class="label">Christ the Redeemer</h3>
          <div class="info">
            <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Christ_the_Redeemer_(statue)" style="text-decoration:none;">Read
              more...</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card" onmouseover="mouseOver5()" onmouseout="mouseOut()">
          <img id="card5" src="images/5.jpg" alt="Image Not Found!" class="img">
          <h3 id="placeLabel5" class="label">Stonehenge</h3>
          <div class="info">
            <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stonehenge" style="text-decoration:none;">Read more...</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card" onmouseover="mouseOver6()" onmouseout="mouseOut()">
          <img id="card6" src="images/6.jpg" alt="Image Not Found!" class="img">
          <h3 id="placeLabel6" class="label">Sydney Opera House</h3>
          <div class="info">
            <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sydney_Opera_House" style="text-decoration:none;">Read more...</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card" onmouseover="mouseOver7()" onmouseout="mouseOut()">
          <img id="card7" src="images/7.jpg" alt="Image Not Found!" class="img">
          <h3 id="placeLabel7" class="label">Great Pyramid of Giza</h3>
          <div class="info">
            <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Great_Pyramid_of_Giza" style="text-decoration:none;">Read more...</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card" onmouseover="mouseOver8()" onmouseout="mouseOut()">
          <img id="card8" src="images/8.jpg" alt="Image Not Found!" class="img">
          <h3 id="placeLabel8" class="label">Grand Canyon</h3>
          <div class="info">
            <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Great_Pyramid_of_Giza" style="text-decoration:none;">Read more...</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card" onmouseover="mouseOver9()" onmouseout="mouseOut()">
          <img id="card9" src="images/9.jpg" alt="Image Not Found!" class="img">
          <h3 id="placeLabel9" class="label">Himeji Castle</h3>
          <div class="info">
            <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Himeji_Castle" style="text-decoration:none;">Read more...</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Dynamic Card Holder -->
        <for(publish in input.published)> 
        <div class="card" onmouseover="mouseOver10()" onmouseout="mouseOut()">
          <img id="card9" src="${publish.image_a}" alt="Image Not Found!" class="img">
          <h3 id="placeLabel9" class="label">${publish.name}</h3>
        </div>
        </for>
        <!-- Dynamic Card Holder -->
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="before-footer">
      <div class="content-footer">
        <span style="font-weight:bold">More About the </span>
        <span style="font-weight:bold; font-style:italic">Let's Go: </span>
        <span>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Sint quia cumque porro fuga fugiat saepe
          consequuntur utr sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Sint quia cumque porro fuga fugiat saepe
          consequuntur ut deserunt earum tempora alias quod similique commodi, incidunt tenetur nihil iste. Laboriosam,
          eos?</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; All rights reserved. Camero | 2018</p>
  </footer>
</body>

